  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1031">
<l>cuḻaṉṟumērp piṉṉa tulaka mataṉā </l>
<l>luḻantu muḻavē talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Agriculture, though laborious, is the most excellent (form of labour); for people, though they go about (in search of various employments), have at last to resort to the farmer.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
